spanGrp.span: I came from the east in Mang'ola
Watoto wangu walikuwa wachungaji wa mifugo
They didn't even study at school
The way to reach this land
I relocated to come to this area
haya deebugeea anin mandan gud asinayi gbaray ng'any
Me and the children we don't have any other work, we are just farming
Haya mimi na watoto hatuna kazi nyingine huwa tunalima
ba hifihifi aa gandaw gew aa deebugees
right now I'm on my own with children
Wa hivi hivi nikiwa peke yangu na watoto
gabaray ng'any gadiyeed nut asinay mandan
Often I am just farming, I don't have any other work
Huwa nalima tu kazi nyingine niliyonayo sina
